<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='334490' id='t-334490'>So it's a lot of vacancy.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:49
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='338090' id='t-338090'>Now some of our audience members</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='340266' id='t-340266'>also tell us about some of the positive things</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='342384' id='t-342384'>that are happening in their communities,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='344429' id='t-344429'>and many of them are banding together</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='346016' id='t-346016'>to take control of some of the vacant lots,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='348122' id='t-348122'>and they're starting community gardens,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='349991' id='t-349991'>which are creating a great sense
