<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='352666' id='t-352666'>but they're very, very clear to tell us</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='354661' id='t-354661'>that this is not enough,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='356452' id='t-356452'>that they want to see their neighborhoods</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='357958' id='t-357958'>return to the way that their
