<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='459899' id='t-459899'>And they also knew that 
they can tap into a workforce</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='462471' id='t-462471'>that was still very skilled in how to make things.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='465997' id='t-465997'>Now we have community stewardship</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='468566' id='t-468566'>happening in neighborhoods,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='470126' id='t-470126'>we have cultural entrepreneurs making decisions</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='472925' id='t-472925'>to move to the city and create enterprises,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='475973' id='t-475973'>and we have businesses relocating,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='477708' id='t-477708'>and this is all in the context</span>
