<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='481366' id='t-481366'>a city that's under the control</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='483167' id='t-483167'>of an emergency manager,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='484789' id='t-484789'>and just this July filed for Chapter 9 bankruptcy.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:20
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='489063' id='t-489063'>So 2010, we started this process, and by 2013,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='492305' id='t-492305'>we released Detroit Future City,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='494389' id='t-494389'>which was our strategic plan to guide the city</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='497227' id='t-497227'>into a better and more prosperous</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='499046' id='t-499046'>and more sustainable existence --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='501323' id='t-501323'>not what it was, but what it could be,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='504988' id='t-504988'>looking at new ways of economic growth,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='508303' id='t-508303'>new forms of land use,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='510284' id='t-510284'>more sustainable and denser neighborhoods,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='513392' id='t-513392'>a reconfigured infrastructure
and city service system,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='516808' id='t-516808'>and a heightened capacity for civic leaders</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='519676' id='t-519676'>to take action and implement change.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='522938' id='t-522938'>Three key imperatives were really important</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='525536' id='t-525536'>to our work.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='526817' id='t-526817'>One was that the city itself
