<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='530695' id='t-530695'>but the economy was too small.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='532383' id='t-532383'>There are only 27 jobs per 100 people in Detroit,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='535643' id='t-535643'>very different from a Denver
