<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='578813' id='t-578813'>where still nearly 300,000 residents lived.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:53
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='582181' id='t-582181'>So we came up with one neighborhood typology --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='584997' id='t-584997'>there are several --
