<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='587970' id='t-587970'>where folks could reappropriate</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='589929' id='t-589929'>abandoned structures</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='591667' id='t-591667'>and turn them into entrepreneurial enterprises,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='593957' id='t-593957'>with a specific emphasis on looking at the, again,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='597040' id='t-597040'>majority 82 percent African-American population.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='600225' id='t-600225'>So they, too, could take businesses</span>
