<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='684768' id='t-684768'>Detroit will not die.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:37
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='686387' id='t-686387'>Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
